Package: csbELISA
Title: Interactive ELISA Data Analysis and Visualization in Shiny
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Caio",
      family = "Santos Bonilha",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "Caio.Bonilha@glasgow.ac.uk"
    )
Description: An open-source R package providing an interactive Shiny-based
    interface for automated ELISA data processing. The package supports
    blank subtraction, standard curve construction via linear regression,
    concentration estimation of unknown samples, data visualization, and
    statistical analysis including group comparisons and multiple-testing
    correction.
